ransvaginal</option>\n<option id=\"T92_301c\" name=\"Transabdominal and transvaginal\" value=\"Transabdominal and transvaginal\">Transabdominal and transvaginal</option>\n</select>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Clinical information\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Clinical information</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_9\" name=\"Clinical information\"> </textarea>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_13\">LMP:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_13\" name=\"LMP\" data-field-type=\"DATE\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_14\">Pregnant:</label>\n<select id=\"T92_14\" name=\"Pregnant\">\n<option id=\"T92_14_15\" name=\"Yes\" value=\"Yes\">Yes</option>\n<option id=\"T92_14_16\" name=\"No\" value=\"No\">No</option>\n<option id=\"T92_14_17\" name=\"Unknown\" value=\"Unknown\">Unknown</option>\n</select>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Comparison\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Comparison</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_19\" name=\"Comparison\">None. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Findings\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Findings</header>\n<section data-section-name=\"Uterus\">\n<header class=\"level2\">Uterus</header>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_24\">Orientation:</label>\n<select id=\"T92_24\" name=\"Orientation\">\n<option id=\"T92_24_25\" name=\"Anteverted\" value=\"Anteverted\">Anteverted</option>\n<option id=\"T92_24_26\" name=\"Retroverted\" value=\"Retroverted\">Retroverted</option>\n</select>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_27\">Size:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_27\" name=\"Size\" value=\"\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_31\">Masses:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_31\" name=\"Masses\" value=\"None.\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_38\">Cervix:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_38\" name=\"Cervix\" value=\"Normal.\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_41\">Endometrium:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_41_text\" name=\"Endometrium\" value=\"Normal.\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_41\">Endometrial thickness:</label>\n<input id=\"T92_41\" type=\"number\" name=\"Endometrial thickness\" value=\"\"/> <label for=\"T92_41\">mm</label>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Adnexa\">\n<header class=\"level2\">Adnexa</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_300\" name=\"Adnexa\">Normal. </textarea>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_48\">Right ovary size:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_48\" name=\"Right ovary size\" value=\"\"/> <label for=\"T92_48\">cm</label>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T92_69\">Left ovary size:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T92_69\" name=\"Left ovary size\" value=\"\"/> <label for=\"T92_69\">cm</label>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Free fluid\">\n<header class=\"level2\">Free fluid</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_127_text\" name=\"Free fluid\">None. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Other findings\">\n<header class=\"level2\">Other findings</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_132\" name=\"Other findings\">None. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Impression\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Impression</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T92_285\" name=\"Impression\"> </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
